nl: tell me about COLISEUM MEDICAL CENTER, LLC	 from above data
sql:
SELECT 
    pr.PROVIDER_ID,
    pr.PROVIDER_GROUP_ID,
    m.NPI,
    m.PROVIDER_NAME,
    m.BILLING_CODE_COUNT,
    m.OVERALL_PCT_OF_AVG,
    ar.ADDRESS,
    ar.CITY,
    ar.STATE,
    ar.PAYER,
    ar.NEGOTIATED_TYPE
FROM 
    "HEALTHCARE_PRICING_ANALYTICS_SAMPLE"."SAMPLES"."PROVIDER_REFERENCES" pr
JOIN 
    "HEALTHCARE_PRICING_ANALYTICS_SAMPLE"."SAMPLES"."METRICS" m ON pr.PROVIDER_ID = m.NPI
JOIN 
    "HEALTHCARE_PRICING_ANALYTICS_SAMPLE"."SAMPLES"."ALL_RATES" ar ON m.NPI = ar.NPI
WHERE 
    m.PROVIDER_NAME = 'COLISEUM MEDICAL CENTER, LLC'
LIMIT 100;
